DISCUSSED IN NOTE A AT THE END OF THE PRECEDING OVERVIEW SECTION. A SUMMARY OF

KEY INFORMATION AND DISCUSSION RELATED TO 3MS GEOGRAPHIC AREAS FOLLOW.

