THE ESTIMATED

COSTS OF ADDRESSING TRACE AMOUNTS OF PERFLUORINATED COMPOUNDS IN DRINKING WATER

SOURCES IN THE CITY OF OAKDALE AND LAKE ELMO, MINNESOTA, AS WELL AS PRESENCE IN

